OL,3,CTeenage boys appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith murder of 'loving father'
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys have appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with the murder of a
OL,8,F"loving father" who was stabbed in
OL,9,FBarry.
OL,11,FThe boys, aged 16 and 17, who cannot
OL,12,Fbe named for legal reasons, were
OL,13,Fremanded into youth detention at
OL,14,FCardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FThursday, 3 July.
OL,17,FThey are charged with the murder of
OL,18,Fmarried father-of-one Kamran Aman, 38,
OL,19,Fwho died in Barry Road just before
OL,20,Fmidnight on Monday.
