OL,3,CTeenage boys appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith murder of 'loving father'
OL,6,FThe boys, who are both from Llantwit
OL,7,FMajor, appeared separately in court.
OL,9,FHead magistrate Patricia Blackwell
OL,10,Fsaid: "The charges which you face are
OL,11,Fso serious that your case must now be
OL,12,Fsent to crown court.
OL,14,F"You will be remanded to youth
OL,15,Fdetention until your appearance at
OL,16,FCardiff Crown Court on Monday."
OL,18,FMr Aman's family released a tribute on
OL,19,FWednesday evening, saying they mourned
OL,20,Fhis loss with "profound sorrow".
