OL,3,CTeenage boys appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith murder of 'loving father'
OL,6,F"A devoted husband, a loving father, a
OL,7,Fcherished son, brother, uncle and
OL,8,Floyal friend, Kamran was the heart of
OL,9,Fhis family and loved within his
OL,10,Fcommunity," they said.
OL,12,F"Known for his generous spirit and
OL,13,Fkind heart, Kamran brought warmth and
OL,14,Fstrength to everyone he met.
OL,16,F"His absence leaves an immeasurable
OL,17,Fvoid in the lives of all who knew him.
OL,19,F"As we grieve this unimaginable loss,
OL,20,Fwe also honour and celebrate the life
OL,21,Fhe lived and the impact he made.
